=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C739 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C1108 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2224%2C1478 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C412\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Canyon CP0018 Aerocockpit wings diagram\" title=\"200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar wings\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C412\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The wings of the CP0018 and CP0015 handlebars can be adjusted for fit or removed for travel.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Canyon</i></span></p></div><p>Canyon founder Roman Arnold said: “Mathieu fortunately did not fall. We want to ensure with absolute certainty that no one comes to harm before we fully understand the root cause.”</p><p>The company’s CEO, Armin Landgraf, added: “We are doing everything we can to equip affected Aeroad models as quickly as possible with a cockpit that meets both our and our customers’ demands for total quality and safety.”</p></section></div>","author":"George Scott","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"330d45bc3b0fa31f9f66982e1adf3993bb2173d